## 2. Core Site Architecture & User Flows

The portfolio will be structured as a high-performance single-page application (SPA) with dedicated, highly detailed sub-routes for case studies to ensure maximum SEO optimization and fast reading speeds.

### 2.1 Site Map
1. **Home Page:** Hero, Core Ethos, Skills Grid, Featured Projects Preview.
2. **Case Study Page Template:** Deep-dives into specific projects like *Bunkie*.
3. **FAQ & Contact Hub:** Dynamic accordion module + frictionless inquiry form.

